	(2089,235,'platform_page_content_7_paragraph','Enable advance query analysis and instantly connect consumer terms to relevant clinical concepts.'),
	(2090,235,'_platform_page_content_7_paragraph','field_533a566d03b34'),
	(2091,235,'platform_page_content_8_headline','Partner Implementations'),
	(2092,235,'_platform_page_content_8_headline','field_533a55ab3eefc'),
	(2093,235,'platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_0_image','292'),
	(2094,235,'_platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_0_image','field_533a55de3eeff'),
	(2095,235,'platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_0_partner_logo','290'),
	(2096,235,'_platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_0_partner_logo','field_533a55f53ef00'),
	(2097,235,'platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_0_paragraph','Microsoft partnered with Healthline to create an anatomical search tool as part of the Bing Health and Fitness application, available via Windows 8.1. The tool is powered by Healthline’s unique taxonomy mappings that readily link body parts to related content, such as symptoms and conditions. Coupled with Healthline’s original health content that was provided in 17 languages, Healthline’s Taxonomy enabled Microsoft to provide an exceptional user experience for its global audience.'),
	(2098,235,'_platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_0_paragraph','field_533a560e3ef01'),
	(2099,235,'platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_1_image','268'),
	(2100,235,'_platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_1_image','field_533a55de3eeff'),
	(2101,235,'platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_1_partner_logo','266'),
	(2102,235,'_platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_1_partner_logo','field_533a55f53ef00'),
	(2103,235,'platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_1_paragraph','IBM Watson technology is being made available to developers world-wide in order to power “Cognitive Apps”, including healthcare solutions that will utilize Healthline’s contextually relevant search tools and content. Amongst these apps is one that IBM Watson is developing to help physicians match patients with the most appropriate treatment plans. IBM Watson is leveraging Healthline’s Taxonomy to enable clinical accurate profiling and search.'),
	(2104,235,'_platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_1_paragraph','field_533a560e3ef01'),
	(2105,235,'platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_2_image','249'),
	(2106,235,'_platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_2_image','field_533a55de3eeff'),
	(2107,235,'platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_2_partner_logo','247'),
	(2108,235,'_platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_2_partner_logo','field_533a55f53ef00'),
	(2109,235,'platform_page_content_8_partner_implementation_2_paragraph','Member portals provide a critical opportunity for payers to improve outcomes and cut costs by steering their members to the right providers. Aetna leveraged Healthline’s taxonomy and search tools to provide an exceptional Provider Search experience for their members. As a result, utilization of the member portal has increased while calls to Member Services decreased.'),
