	(6438,214,'search_discovery_page_content_7_partner_implementations_0_paragraph','Member portals provide a critical opportunity for payers to improve outcomes and cut costs by steering their members to the right providers. Aetna leveraged Healthline’s taxonomy and search tools to provide an exceptional Provider Search experience for their members. As a result, utilization of the member portal has increased while calls to Member Services decreased.'),
	(6439,214,'_search_discovery_page_content_7_partner_implementations_0_paragraph','field_533b50c72a473'),
