	(6444,214,'search_discovery_page_content_7_partner_implementations_1_paragraph','Elsevier is the world’s largest medical publisher. Their library includes more than 250 Million documents that are stored in disparate locations and formats. Healthline’s Taxonomy and Search technology made it possible for doctors, nurses, and researchers to search and access this massive library from a single interface, called Clinical Key.'),
	(6445,214,'_search_discovery_page_content_7_partner_implementations_1_paragraph','field_533b50c72a473'),
