	(6450,214,'search_discovery_page_content_7_partner_implementations_2_paragraph','Yahoo! needed a domain expert to power its health channel and provide exceptional search tools in order to maximize consumer engagement. Healthline built and hosts Yahoo! Health, a fully integrated portal which receives over 20 million unique visitors per month. Since its partnership with Healthline, Yahoo! has achieved consistent annual increases in health ad revenue.'),
