	(9353,471,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_1_position','field_533c6ddeeba9f'),
	(9354,471,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_1_bio','Richard Harroch joined VantagePoint in 2003 from Orrick, Herrington & Sutcliffe LLP, bringing with him an extensive body of transactional and business expertise. He is a successful entrepreneur, founder and Chairman of two companies: LawCommerce.com (sold to LexisNexis) and Allbusiness.com (sold to Dun and Bradstreet.)'),
	(9355,471,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_1_bio','field_533c6de5ebaa0'),
