	(14205,483,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_1_bio','Richard Harroch joined VantagePoint in 2003 from Orrick, Herrington & Sutcliffe LLP, bringing with him an extensive body of transactional and business expertise. He is a successful entrepreneur, founder and Chairman of two companies: LawCommerce.com (sold to LexisNexis) and Allbusiness.com (sold to Dun and Bradstreet.)'),
	(14206,483,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_1_bio','field_533c6de5ebaa0'),
	(14207,483,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_2_name','Michael Barber'),
